<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊、潘瑟和鲍比盯着简。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你刚刚是许愿要翅膀吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊不敢相信地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简的眼里涌出了泪花，她点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直都很想飞。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然间每个人都开始说话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯嗯。”休伊清了清嗓子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没人注意他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，休伊用力拍了拍手掌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，打扰一下。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“简的愿望是飞翔。现在取消她的愿望已经太迟了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊交叉双臂靠在了他的壳上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我的后背好痒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比试图将手够到背后去挠痒痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”赛伊扭过头去看自己的背。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个白色的小包在他的背上鼓了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们开始不断长大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快孩子们看上去每个人的背上都背了一个巨大的白色的包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我的天啊！”潘瑟低声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有翅膀了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她摆动着背上白色的翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>羽毛飞得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们要怎么才能飞？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别看我。”他说，“我的鳍又不是用来飞的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊说着又消失在了他的壳里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊将那个壳送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，其他孩子正在努力试着使用他们的翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比闭着眼睛，握紧了拳头使劲，脸憋得通红。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看上去是需要去厕所。”简咯咯笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，那你来试试。”鲍比涨红了脸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简闭上了双眼，静静地长长吐了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她背上的两个隆起物张开了，就像雨伞被打开那样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们变成了美丽的天使翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些翅膀约有三米宽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇哦！”其他的孩子们惊奇地大叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简昂起头，弯曲了膝盖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她用双脚轻轻蹬了一下地面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当简跳起来的时候，她的翅膀就开始拍打起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要飞了！我要飞了！”简激动地叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的兄弟姐妹们也跟着她做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的翅膀一个接一个地打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，他们就在天空中与简会合了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“简！”潘瑟大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我们到今天为止许过的最好的愿望！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简对着自己的姐姐微笑了一下，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后开始朝着太阳飞得更高了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，看！”鲍比向下指着地面说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他们的下方是他们住的那个村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们可以看到人们在街道上走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们看上去和虫子一样小。”赛伊笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是玛莎阿姨的房子！”潘瑟指着前方说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们像一群鸟一样慢慢地朝着那个方向飞过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨在那儿呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊用一只手挡在眼睛上方向下看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在种花。”潘瑟补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，那是我们的小宝宝，兰姆！”简大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们清楚地看到兰姆坐在毯子上玩儿着他的玩具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨！兰姆！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比突然开始挥舞着他的双臂大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比！不要！”赛伊抓住了鲍比的手臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为男孩子们在相互争论，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们忘记了继续拍打他们的翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”赛伊和鲍比开始往下掉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆听见了熟悉的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比！赛伊！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你刚刚是叫了你的哥哥们的名字吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨自豪地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊。鲍比 。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆用他圆圆胖胖的小胳膊指着天空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>363106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊！鲍比！”潘瑟和简大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>363107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“继续挥动你们的翅膀啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>373572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但男孩们却直直的往下落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>